# Xcind auto-includes a gitignored `.override` sibling for each env file
# (docs/guides/env-files.md). Local-only overrides — e.g. this developer's
# public MERCURE_PUBLIC_URL in .env.docker.dev.override — never get committed.
.env.override
.env.*.override
